## Default barplot

We can look at the relative performance of the candidates within each state using a nested bar plot.

::: {.cell execution_count=3}
``` {.python .cell-code}
ax = sns.barplot(
    data = df_swing, 
    x = 'state', 
    y = 'pct_estimate', 
    hue = 'candidate_name')
```

