## Altering the axes

Altering the axis increases the distance between the bars. Some might say that is misleading.

::: {.cell execution_count=4}
``` {.python .cell-code}
ax = sns.barplot(
    data = df_swing, 
    x = 'state', 
    y = 'pct_estimate', 
    hue = 'candidate_name')

ax.set(ylim=(41, 52))
```

