We can do the same thing in Altair.

::: {.cell execution_count=6}
``` {.python .cell-code}
alt.Chart(df_swing).mark_bar().encode(
    x='candidate_name',
    y='pct_estimate',
    color='candidate_name',
    column = alt.Column('state:O', spacing = 5, header = alt.Header(labelOrient = "bottom")),
)
```

